# Maven Documentation

## Project Metadata
- `<name>`, `<description>`, `<url>` in every POM
- `<developers>` and `<licenses>` in root POM
- `<scm>` pointing to the repository

## Javadoc Plugin
- Configure `maven-javadoc-plugin` in `<reporting>` section
- Fail on warnings for public API modules: `<failOnWarnings>true</failOnWarnings>`
- Link to external Javadoc: `<links>` for JDK, Spring, Jakarta

## Site Generation
- `maven-site-plugin` for project documentation site
- Include: project info, dependency reports, Javadoc, test reports, coverage
- JaCoCo report integration for coverage visualization

